    "en": {
      "title": "Tomorrow evening the rooster will crow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka Labor Congress will hold a virtual meeting tomorrow (19) to decide who to vote for, Congress General Secretary Member of Parliament Jeevan Thondaman has said.",
        "He posted a Twitter post and mentioned that as the general secretary, he will request the executive committee to allow professionals from the highlands to share their unbiased views.",
        "After that, we will announce tomorrow (19) evening about whom we will support in voting for the presidential election."
      ],
